graph TD
    Start([Start: User Story Testing Infrastructure]) --> Phase1

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 1: CLI Enhancements
    %% ========================================
    Phase1{Phase 1: CLI Enhancements} --> US_001

    US_001[US_001: Update stories find for plan-local<br/>Agent: build-python<br/>Target: commands/stories.py] --> US_001_Check{Success?}
    US_001_Check -->|Yes| US_002
    US_001_Check -->|No| US_001_Fix[Fix Issues]
    US_001_Fix --> US_001

    US_002[US_002: Implement agentic stories init<br/>Agent: build-python<br/>Target: commands/stories.py] --> US_002_Check{Success?}
    US_002_Check -->|Yes| US_003
    US_002_Check -->|No| US_002_Fix[Fix Issues]
    US_002_Fix --> US_002

    US_003[US_003: Implement agentic stories cat<br/>Agent: build-python<br/>Target: commands/stories.py] --> US_003_Check{Success?}
    US_003_Check -->|Yes| Phase2
    US_003_Check -->|No| US_003_Fix[Fix Issues]
    US_003_Fix --> US_003

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 2: Agent Guidance Integration
    %% ========================================
    Phase2{Phase 2: Agent Guidance Integration} --> US_004

    US_004[US_004: Update test-audit agent guidance<br/>Agent: teacher-update-guidance<br/>Target: test-audit/process.yml] --> US_004_Check{Success?}
    US_004_Check -->|Yes| TestPhase
    US_004_Check -->|No| US_004_Fix[Fix Issues]
    US_004_Fix --> US_004

    %% ========================================
    %% TEST PHASE: Validation
    %% ========================================
    TestPhase{Test Phase: Validation} --> RunTests

    RunTests[Run CLI tests<br/>Agent: test-runner<br/>Target: pytest commands] --> TestFixLoop

    %% ========================================
    %% LOOP: Test-Fix Loop
    %% ========================================
    TestFixLoop{Test-Fix Loop<br/>Iteration Counter}
    TestFixLoop -->|All Pass| AuditLoop
    TestFixLoop -->|Failures Found| TestFix[Builder fixes failures]
    TestFix --> RunTests
    TestFixLoop -->|Max 5 Iterations| Escalate1[Escalate to User:<br/>Test failures persist]

    %% ========================================
    %% LOOP: Audit-Test-Fix Loop (MANDATORY)
    %% ========================================
    AuditLoop{Audit-Test-Fix Loop<br/>Iteration Counter}
    AuditLoop -->|First Run| Audit[Test Auditor:<br/>Verify stories commands work]
    Audit --> AuditCheck{Audit Pass?}
    AuditCheck -->|Yes & Tests Pass| Complete
    AuditCheck -->|Issues Found| AuditFix[Fix audit issues]
    AuditFix --> RunTests
    AuditLoop -->|Max 3 Iterations| Escalate2[BLOCK Completion:<br/>Audit failures must be resolved]

    %% ========================================
    %% COMPLETION
    %% ========================================
    Complete([Complete: User Story Infrastructure Ready])

    %% ========================================
    %% SUCCESS CRITERIA
    %% ========================================
    %% - agentic stories find discovers stories in global and plan-local directories
    %% - agentic stories init creates a valid YAML template
    %% - test-audit agent can walk through a user story as a blind test

